<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-MoRNloxbStBcD8z3M/2BmnT+rg4IsMxPkXaGh2zD6LGNNFE80W3onsAhRcMAMrSoyWL9xD7Ert0men7vR8LUZg=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <title>Motion on Notice</title>
</head>

<style>
    html,
    body {
        font-size: 12px;
        margin: 10px 15px;
        font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;

    }

    .text-center {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .top-heading h6 {
        margin: 0;
    }

    h6 {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        font-weight: bold;
        line-height: normal;

    }
</style>

<body id="draft" class="text-justify">
    <div>
        <div class="top-heading">
            <div class=" my-3 text-center heading text-uppercase">
                <h6>
                    IN THE HIGH COURT OF {{state_arrest}}
                </h6>
                <h6>IN THE {{state_arrest}} JUDICIAL DIVISION</h6>
                <h6>HOLDEN AT {{state_arrest}}</h6>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right text-uppercase my-3">
                SUIT NO:        /FHR/{{year}}
            </div>
            <div class="text-justify text-dark text-uppercase">
                IN THE MATTER OF AN APPLICATION FOR THE ENFORCEMENT OF THE APPLICANT’S
                FUNDAMENTAL RIGHTS TO RESPECT FOR THE DIGNITY OF HIS PERSON, PERSONAL
                LIBERTY, RIGHT TO FAIR TRIAL WITHIN A REASONABLE TIME AND FREEDOM OF
                MOVEMENT.
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2 font-weight-bold">BETWEEN</div>
            <div class="flex justify-content-between text-uppercase">
                <div>{{name}}</div>
                <div class="font-weight-bold">APPLICANT</div>
            </div>
            <div class="my-2">AND</div>
            <ol class="text-uppercase">
                <li>THE ATTORNEY GENERAL, {{state_arrest}}</li>
                <li>
                    <Flex>
                        <div class="flex-1 ">
                            THE COMMISSIONER OF POLICE, {{state_arrest}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-uppercase text-bold ">RESPONDENT</div>
                    </Flex>
                                     
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div className="body">
            <h6 className="text-center" align="center">MOTION ON NOTICE</h6>
            <h6 className="text-uppercase">
                APPLICATION TO ADMIT TO BAIL THE ACCUSED/APPLICANT {{name}}
                BROUGHT PURSUANT TO SECTIONS 35(4) AND 36 OF THE CONSTITUTION OF THE
                FEDERAL REPUBLIC OF NIGERIA, 1999 (AS AMENDED AND UNDER THE INHERENT
                JURISDICTION OF THE COURT.
            </h6>
            <div>
                <p>
                    TAKE NOTICE: that this Honourable Court will be moved on
                    _________________________day of ______________________________
                    {{year}} at the Hour of 9 O.clock in the
                    forenoon or so soon thereafter as the Applicant or Counsel on
                    behalf of the Applicant may be heard praying this honourable court
                    for the following reliefs:
                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        AN ORDER of the Honourable Court admitting to bail the
                        Accused/Applicant who is now in prison custody pending trial.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        AND for such further or other Order(s) as this Honourable Court
                        may deem fit to make in the circumstance.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="footer">
            <div class="mt-5">
                Dated this ____________ day of ______________________
                {{year}}
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-end">
                <div>
                    <div>G.B. EVANS, ESQ</div>
                    <div>Evans Dule’s Foundation </div>
                    <div>Solicitor to the Accused/Applicant</div>
                    <div>No. 163A Okporo Road Port Harcourt,</div>
                    <div>Rivers State.</div>
                    <div>Email: evansb45@yahoo.com</div>
                    <div> 08107639372</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="footer-left">
                    <h6>FOR SERVICE ON:</h6>      
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            <div>Attorney General, {{state_arrest}},</div>
                            <div>Ministry of Justice ,</div>
                            <div>Secretariat</div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div>Commissioner of Police, {{state_arrest}},</div>
                            <div>{{state_arrest}} Police Command,</div>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                          
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>